content:
Extract detailed insights from CRM Analytics that support collaboration and informed decision-making. You can download images and filtered data from lens explorations and dashboard widgets. Download formats include image (.png), Microsoft Excel (.xls), and comma-separated values (.csv) files.

Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience, with CRM Analytics in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions for an extra cost. Also available in Developer Edition.

To download data from widgets and lenses using the CRM Analytics user interface: Download CRM Analytics Data. To share images of dashboards and widgets when Secure Image Sharing and Downloading is enabled: Share CRM Analytics Images

When downloading data in Excel or CSV format, note that:

* The query limit determines the number of rows in the .xls or .csv file.
* Exports to Excel files are limited to 6,000,000 cells.
* Downloads aren't supported for lenses based on SQL queries or direct data queries.
* Text wrapping within tables isn't supported.
* Columns and cells may not be exported as expected due to limitations.
title: Downloading Data from Salesforce Analytics
